{"tid":1808385,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲青年藏兩支汽油彈 今認罪判囚一年","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T13:22:49.000Z","uid":282079,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e4be9c07a5b030a90601c0a780b29e349e5ebe","tid":1808385,"uid":282079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"網民於10月13日在多區商場發起「神獸罷鷲」行動，並有人在將軍澳區堵路放火。其間警方追截一名22歲青年，在其背囊內發現兩支汽油彈。青年今在裁判法院承認在公眾地方藏有攻擊性武器罪，求情指擔心監禁影響前途，亦明白政治問題不應透過暴力解決。最終他被判監一年，是反送中抗爭運動以來首次有人因藏有汽油彈而被判監。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉嘉柏（22歲）今承認於去年10月13日在將軍澳尚德廣場2樓6號及7號升降機的公眾地方攜有攻擊性武器，即兩支汽油彈、一個火機、一罐液化丁烷氣、一個噴嘴及一個鎚仔。被告的母親聞判後哭成淚人，需身旁親友安慰。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200102&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60443408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200102%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60443408&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPpFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=78e03d47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200102%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60443408&h=15fc2620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200102&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60443408</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0868f8307c8c666d1c30c4033a6842b73d5e1c","tid":1808385,"uid":160991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a5ebe4ed9077b7b8cd6812fd3783eb9937703f84","tid":1808385,"uid"